OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 20 APR
OL,4,CCHANNELS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1964FBBC TV is renamed BBC One,
OL,7,Ffollowing the launch of BBC Two. The
OL,8,Fchannel's on-screen identity is updated
OL,9,Fwith the introduction of a new globe
OL,10,Fsymbol (the second globe device).
OL,11,
OL,12,CG2009FBBC Parliament's on-screen
OL,13,Fpresentation is updated to bring it
OL,14,Finto line with the core BBC TV News
OL,15,Fbranding, first seen a year earlier.
OL,16,FBoth packages were produced by
OL,17,FLambie-Nairn.
